import React from 'react'
import AllServices from './AllServices'
import Footer from './Footer'
import NavBar from './NavBar'
import SearchServices from './SearchServices'
import Test from './Test'

export default function App() {
  return (
    <>
    <NavBar />
    <SearchServices />
    <AllServices />
    <Test/>
    <Footer/>
    </>
  )
}
